{"tid":1823920,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林鄭：不認同改動單程證政策","createTime":"2020-01-14T05:18:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-14T06:49:14.000Z","uid":267488,"like":1,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"21d93fa6e649955c1ce19f417a7d399cf8ebb5ac","tid":1823920,"uid":267488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T05:18:35.000Z","msg":"新地執行董事郭基煇在廣東省政協會議提出，將單程證上限由每日150個削減一半。行政長官林鄭月娥指，單程證是用作家庭團聚，現時跨境婚姻仍處高水平，不認同要改動現有政策。 <br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥：「跨境婚姻在高水平，有三分一是跨境，上述種種都說明要有入境政策。此時改動這個政策或名額，會帶出一個訊息，我們將社會上見到個別問題或現象推向單程證家庭團聚政策，不是我們考慮的方案。」<br />\n<br />\n林鄭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50b6ca91a8a384a927090b78de7abefd1fb085e8","tid":1823920,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T05:19:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e12343339ec81ff489192f9c898c8bcc87594dc0","tid":1823920,"uid":27664,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T05:23:52.000Z","msg":"香港人應該要自己攞返做主動權話事，777冇用信可言"},{"pid":"0398be4ce847b6f264522e48b352a82920f69c65","tid":1823920,"uid":130406,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T05:24:47.000Z","msg":"點解一定要團聚呢?  <br />\n分開吓都幾好架<br />\n無得見未學識吓照顧自己"},{"pid":"df5637a4455406c0fb15e94e3a6e5ea2e0855288","tid":1823920,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T05:27:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">歐美議員講野又無人理啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n響task1 &amp;2呀 幫手啦上唔到千呀</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>Twitter組24小時keep住更新</strong></span><br />\n幫手retweet <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2F